title: Kim Kardashian West is a Carpool Mom
author: TheEllenShow
description:
Kim Kardashian West called herself a "carpool mom," describing how she has to wrangle multiple kids to bring them to school in the mornings. The reality TV star explained the personality differences between her four kids and shared what it's like to see her mom Kris Jenner and Ellen partying together.
